desc: Performance meets fashion with Amade Swim®. High quality athletic inspired men's and women's swimwear as well as sporty cover-ups for both. Proudly made in New York City. The only place to buy Amade Swim® is directly through our website. Accept no imitations!

layout.text: Inspired by the can do American Spirit, we set out to create a swimwear collection that embodies the quality, pride and sportsmanship of this sport. Being exclusively American made has and continues to be our mission.
